snippet.title: Session: Skate Sim | Ride with the Ninja Turtles - Free Update
snippet.description:
TMNT are coming to Session: Skate Sim! Show off your skateboarding skills in a brand new map : The Sewers from the legendary Teenage Mutant Turtles.

The TMNT update is free and available now on Session: Skate Sim.

Session: Skate Sim is available on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, and on PC (Steam/Epic Games Store).
